Revision history for Perl extension Term::ANSIColor::Print.

0.06  Sun Jan 31 15:39:59 2010
    - trailing _ omits the eol
    - carp instead of warn about unknown tokens
    - multi-token aliases

0.05  Sun Dec 27 10:09:37 2009
    - Changed default options: eol => "\n", output => \*STDOUT
    - Added alias option

0.04  Thu Sep 03 18:21:55 2009
    - Refinements to examples
    - Unlimited length method parsing

0.03  Wed Sep 02 23:58:24 2009
    - Added checkerboard sample
    - Updated old glory sample

0.02  Tue Sep 01 23:32:09 2009
    - Much sweeter sample program outputs Old Glory

0.01  Mon Aug 31 21:59:54 2009
    - original version; created by h2xs 1.23 with options
    -XA -n Term::ANSIColor::Print

